---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const isLanding = true;
---

<BaseLayout title="Partner Tecnológico B2B para Startups y Empresas | VortexLM" isLanding={isLanding}>
  <main class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">

    <!-- HERO SECTION (refactorizada) -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950 px-6">
      <!-- Grid overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:64px_64px] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_110%)]"></div>
      <!-- Glow orb -->
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 via-white/[0.02] to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center pt-32 pb-24">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-800 rounded-full text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-8">Partner Tecnológico</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-extralight tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.08] max-w-4xl mx-auto opacity-95">
          Cobro por horas eficientes.<br/>
          Transparencia total.<br/>
          <span class="text-neutral-400">Para startups y empresas en Madrid y Barcelona.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Contratas ingeniería de alto rendimiento sin pagar por horas muertas ni sorpresas en la factura. 
          Cada minuto de desarrollo se registra en tu <strong class="text-white/80">Panel de Control</strong> en tiempo real: 
          contador de horas exactas trabajadas, control de tareas del sprint y estado del proyecto. 
          Paga solo por lo que realmente se invierte en tu producto.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/contacto" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-all text-center duration-200 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)]">
            Solicitar consultoría gratuita
          </a>
          <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="document.querySelector('.live-chat-trigger')?.click()" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-3 border border-neutral-800 text-neutral-300 font-medium text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-900 transition-all text-center duration-200">
            ¿Dudas rápidas? Háblanos por el chat →
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-600">Madrid · Barcelona · Sin permanencia · Sin mínimos</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUST BAR -->
    <section class="border-t border-b border-neutral-900 py-8 bg-neutral-950/50">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-600 text-center mb-6">Especialistas en</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 text-neutral-700">
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">STARTUPS</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">SaaS</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">FINTECH</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">E-COMMERCE</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest">ENTERPRISE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3-COLUMN SERVICES -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-black border-b border-neutral-900">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-800 rounded-full text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-6">Capacidades Técnicas</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Ingeniería de primer nivel<br/><span class="text-neutral-400">para tu negocio</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all mb-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Performance Estricto (100/100)</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Eliminamos la pérdida de leads optimizando Core Web Vitals al máximo. Puntuaciones perfectas en Lighthouse y PageSpeed Insights garantizadas.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all mb-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Stack Moderno y Escalable</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Astro, Next.js, React, Node.js, TypeScript. Arquitecturas limpias con SSR, ISR y Edge Functions para máxima velocidad y escalabilidad.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-full aspect-[4/3] linear-card rounded border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/30 flex items-center justify-center p-6 glow-hover transition-all mb-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2.5">Ciberseguridad y Compliance</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Desarrollo con estándares OWASP, cifrado SSL/TLS, autenticación segura y cumplimiento GDPR para operar en Europa sin riesgos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN: Transparencia Radical – Panel de Control de Cliente -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-black border-b border-neutral-900">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-800 rounded-full text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-6">Transparencia</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Transparencia Radical<br/><span class="text-neutral-400">Panel de Control de Cliente</span></h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
            Olvídate de las incertidumbres. Nuestro panel privado te da visibilidad absoluta de cada minuto invertido, cada tarea completada y cada euro gastado. En tiempo real.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
          <!-- Card Panel 1: Contador de horas en tiempo real -->
          <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/60 hover:bg-neutral-950/90 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-neutral-700 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 group-hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">Contador de horas exactas trabajadas</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Olvídate de estimaciones hinchadas. Cada tarea registra el tiempo real de desarrollo con un temporizador que se sincroniza automáticamente con tu panel. Ves exactamente cuánto tiempo ha llevado cada cosa, quién trabajó y qué se hizo.
            </p>
            <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06]">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Sprint actual — Rediseño Dashboard</span>
                <span class="text-[11px] font-mono text-neutral-400">12.4h / 20h estimadas</span>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full h-2 rounded-full bg-white/[0.06] overflow-hidden">
                <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-emerald-400" style="width:62%"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-white/[0.04]">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"></span>
                  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-emerald-500"></span>
                </span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400/80">Seguimiento activo ahora</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card Panel 2: Control de tareas del sprint -->
          <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/60 hover:bg-neutral-950/90 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-neutral-700 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 group-hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">Control de tareas del sprint</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Visualiza el kanban de tu proyecto en vivo: tareas pendientes, en progreso, en revisión y completadas. Cada tarea muestra su responsable, horas invertidas y estado. Ajusta prioridades sobre la marcha.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06]">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full border-2 border-yellow-500/50 bg-yellow-500/20 shrink-0"></div>
                <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 flex-1">Header responsive</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-500">3.2h</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-yellow-400/70">En progreso</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06]">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-500/50 bg-blue-500/20 shrink-0"></div>
                <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 flex-1">Integración pasarela pago</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-500">—</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400/70">Pendiente</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06]">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full border-2 border-emerald-500/50 bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-2 h-2 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 flex-1">Optimización SEO blog</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-500">1.0h</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400/70">Completado</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card Panel 3: Estado del proyecto -->
          <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/60 hover:bg-neutral-950/90 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-neutral-700 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 group-hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 016 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0110.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 016 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 013.75 18v-2.25zM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0120.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6zM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 012.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0118 20.25h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0113.5 18v-2.25z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">Estado del proyecto en tiempo real</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Dashboard con métricas clave: porcentaje de avance del sprint, horas consumidas vs. presupuestadas, próximos hitos y entregas programadas. Siempre sabrás dónde está tu proyecto.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] text-center">
                <span class="block text-xl font-light text-white">62%</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Avance</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] text-center">
                <span class="block text-xl font-light text-white">12.4h</span>
                <span class="text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">Consumidas</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Card Panel 4: Control de facturas LLC -->
          <div class="group relative p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/60 hover:bg-neutral-950/90 transition-all duration-500 hover:border-neutral-700 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 group-hover:border-neutral-600 transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-neutral-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3">Control de facturas LLC sin sorpresas</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Cada factura emitida desde Vortex Logic LLC (EE.UU.) está respaldada por el registro de horas de tu panel. Revisa, descarga y concilia tus facturas con los datos reales de consumo. <strong class="text-white/80">Sin cargos ocultos, sin desviaciones.</strong>
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl bg-emerald-950/20 border border-emerald-900/30">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400/80 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-xs text-emerald-300/80">Facturación basada en horas reales registradas. 0% IVA para empresas españolas (inversión del sujeto pasivo).</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA de la sección -->
        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 font-light mb-6">¿Quieres ver cómo funciona el panel en vivo?</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contacto" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-all text-center duration-200">
              Solicita una demo del panel
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="document.querySelector('.live-chat-trigger')?.click()" class="px-8 py-3 border border-neutral-800 text-neutral-300 font-medium text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-900 transition-all text-center duration-200">
              O escríbenos por el chat web para una respuesta al instante
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN: Desarrollo WordPress de Alto Nivel para tus Proyectos de Kit Digital -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-black border-b border-neutral-900">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1.5 border border-neutral-800 rounded-full text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-6">WordPress Enterprise</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">Desarrollo WordPress de Alto Nivel<br/><span class="text-neutral-400">para tus Proyectos de Kit Digital</span></h2>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
            ¿Tienes aprobados bonos de Kit Digital pero tu equipo no da abasto para maquetar? 
            Nosotros nos encargamos de la ingeniería. Tú gestionas al cliente y la burocracia; 
            nosotros construimos las webs con <strong class="text-white/80">código impecable, Pixel-Perfect</strong> y optimizadas 
            para superar cualquier auditoría técnica del programa. Sin page builders, sin plantillas, sin sorpresas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
          <!-- Card 1: Cumplimiento de Requisitos Oficiales -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/40 hover:bg-neutral-950/70 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2">Cumplimiento de Requisitos Oficiales</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Estructuras adaptadas 100% a las exigencias del Kit Digital: Accesibilidad nivel AA (WCAG 2.1), SEO básico on-page, diseño responsive y paneles autogestionables listos para auditoría.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 2: Velocidad de Entrega (Sprints) -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/40 hover:bg-neutral-950/70 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2">Velocidad de Entrega (Sprints)</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Desbloquea tu flujo de caja. Entregamos las webs listas para revisión en tiempo récord para que puedas justificar el bono ante el Ministerio sin retrasos administrativos.</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Card 3: Código Limpio y WPO -->
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-900 bg-neutral-950/40 hover:bg-neutral-950/70 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 rounded-lg bg-white/[0.04] border border-neutral-800 flex items-center justify-center">
